media: vsp1: Add support for missing 32-bit RGB formats

Add support for the V4L2_PIX_FMT_BGRA32, V4L2_PIX_FMT_BGRX32,
V4L2_PIX_FMT_RGBA32 and V4L2_PIX_FMT_RGBX32 formats to the VSP driver.

